Sentencas: The Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta (SSC) cathode was fabricated under slightly overfired condition and was in situ treated with 25% CO2(V/V) under single cell operating circumstance.
Titulo: Effect of CO2 treatment on the performance of SM0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode electrocatalyst

Sentencas: XRD and TG analysis demonstrated that some SrCO3 and Co3O4, appeared on the SSC surface after CO2 treatment at 600 V. The existence of SrCoO3-delta and Co3O4 under air sweep condition resulted in the changes of physicochemical properties of cathode surface to some extent.
Titulo: Effect of CO2 treatment on the performance of SM0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode electrocatalyst

Sentencas: The acceleration of oxygen reduction rate of the cathode electrocatalyst evidently decreased the polarization resistance and consequently yielded about 20 % higher cell performance than the untreated one.
Titulo: Effect of CO2 treatment on the performance of SM0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ cathode electrocatalyst
